trans-unit.source: When used as a resource key for a data template, allows the data template to participate in the lookup process.
trans-unit.target: 當做資料範本的資源索引鍵使用時，可讓資料範本參與查閱處理序。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Type> that specifies the type of object that the template is used to display, or a string that specifies the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xml-md.md)] tag name for the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xml-md.md)] data that the template is used to display.
